# Cloudflare Pages redirects.
# Docs: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/

# Enforce non-www as the canonical domain. Cloudflare Pages applies path
# redirects from this file; host-level redirects are also handled by
# functions/_middleware.ts so the canonical rule still works if Pages ignores
# absolute-source redirect rules.
https://www.mypayrights.com https://mypayrights.com 301
https://www.mypayrights.com/* https://mypayrights.com/:splat 301
http://www.mypayrights.com https://mypayrights.com 301
http://www.mypayrights.com/* https://mypayrights.com/:splat 301
